{"id":688209,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maurice_Pon","text":"Maurice Marie Jean Pon (26 October 1921 \u2013 3 April 2019) was a French lyricist. He was best known for his work with Henri Salvador. He also wrote for artists such as Bourvil, Fernandel, Jean Sablon, Andr\u00E9 Claveau and Les Fr\u00E8res Jacques. He was born in Bordeaux.\nPon died on 3 April 2019 in \u00CEle-de-France. He was 97.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"French_people","surface_form":"French","offset":62},{"uri":"Lyricist","surface_form":"lyricist","offset":69},{"uri":"Henri_Salvador","surface_form":"Henri Salvador","offset":115},{"uri":"Bourvil","surface_form":"Bourvil","offset":165},{"uri":"Fernandel","surface_form":"Fernandel","offset":174},{"uri":"Jean_Sablon","surface_form":"Jean Sablon","offset":185},{"uri":"Andr%C3%A9_Claveau","surface_form":"Andr\u00E9 Claveau","offset":198},{"uri":"Les_Fr%C3%A8res_Jacques","surface_form":"Les Fr\u00E8res Jacques","offset":216},{"uri":"Bordeaux","surface_form":"Bordeaux","offset":251},{"uri":"%C3%8Ele-de-France","surface_form":"\u00CEle-de-France","offset":289}]}